Yeah, walk away, Cooper.

49
00:02:25,795 --> 00:02:26,921
Big Daddy's not your problem.

50
00:02:27,063 --> 00:02:28,530
[BOY CRIES]

51
00:02:29,499 --> 00:02:31,626
- Have another kid we don't know about?
- Funny.

52
00:02:31,768 --> 00:02:34,498
- This is Julian.
- It's the CF family's, Sam.

53
00:02:34,637 --> 00:02:36,161
Champ, come here.

54
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,497
It is just wrong.

55
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:41,041
A single father, two kids,
and all of them have cystic fibrosis.

56
00:02:41,177 --> 00:02:43,839
And Julian's father
doesn't sound so good.

57
00:02:49,886 --> 00:02:52,081
ADDISON:
Hey, you two. Is this photography day?

58
00:02:52,222 --> 00:02:54,087
DARON: Yeah. I got Gracie a camera
for her birthday.

59
00:02:54,224 --> 00:02:56,215
