of everything.

60
00:02:56,359 --> 00:02:57,621
[ADDISON CHUCKLES]

61
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,728
- Oh, sure.
- I'm making a scrapbook.

62
00:03:00,029 --> 00:03:01,121
